This project is a port of NetBSD's mtree utility to Linux.

Notes:

- Information about the original NetBSD version:
  https://cdn.netbsd.org/pub/pkgsrc/current/pkgsrc/pkgtools/mtree/README.html

- This build requires the "libnbcompat" library, available here:
  https://github.com/archiecobbs/libnbcompat
